![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/c11573fd-5ac9-4347-a0be-07658887b23a/e302.jpg)

Marvel's Spider-Man 2, one of the most highly anticipated sequels in video game history has been released and has taken over the world! That means, its a PERFECT time to go over the events that got us here with a recap and review of Marvel's Spider-Man and its spin-off Spider-Man: Miles Morales! We even manage to do a spoiler-free review of the latest release, so check it out!  
  
Please leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us wherever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by **ComicBook Clique**, the only stop for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.  

